  },
  {
    title: "Progressive Disclosure",
    description:
      "L0(JSX) → L1(hooks) → L2(resources) → L3(frame) → L4(raw Phaser)。必要に応じて段階的に低レベルAPIへ。",
  },
  {
    title: "Rich Hooks & Behaviors",
    description:
      "useTween, useSpring, useStateMachine等のhooksとSpring, Oscillate等の宣言的behaviors。",
  },
  {
    title: "Scene Management",
    description:
      "Phaserのシーンスタックをコンポーネントとして管理。Preload, Overlay等の専用コンポーネント付き。",
  },
  {
    title: "TypeScript First",
    description:
      "完全な型定義でPhaser GameObjectの全プロパティに型安全なアクセス。",
  },
];
